---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="页面未找到 · Azek431"
  description="这个页面不存在，可以返回首页、项目页或搜索页继续浏览。"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="not-found">
      <h1 style="position: relative;">
        404
        <span
          style="
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: var(--gradient-accent);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            filter: blur(20px);
            opacity: 0.4;
            z-index: -1;
          "
        ></span>
      </h1>
      <p>
        你访问的页面可能已经移动、删除，或者暂时还没有创建。可以返回首页继续浏览 Azek431
        的个人主站。
      </p>

      <div class="not-found__actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="/projects/">查看项目</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="/search/">站内搜索</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
